00432 string toString(vector<pair<string, vector<string>>> v)
00433 {
00434   stringstream buffer;
00435   buffer << "[";
00436   for (size_t i = 0, S = v.size(); i < S; ++i) {
00437     buffer << "[" << v[i].first;
00438     buffer << ", Set[";
00439     for (size_t j = 0, S = v[i].second.size(); j < S; ++j) {
00440       buffer << v[i].second[j];
00441       if (j < S-1) {
00442         buffer << ", ";
00443       }
00444     }
00445     buffer << "]]";
00446     if (i < S-1) {
00447       buffer << ", ";
00448     }
00449   }
00450   buffer << "]";
00451   return buffer.str();
00452 }
